P2RE® Crowdfunding
Peer Real Estate Lending Marketplace

Deal Sourcing

We work with experienced, vetted real estate operators with the best projects and opportunities for funding.


Due Diligence

We ensure that borrowers and Projects meet our stringent risk profiles and high underwriting standards using our technology, data analytics, and vast real estate experience.


Prefunding

We put our own skin in the game, quickly funding projects so borrowers can get right to work, and investors begin earning interest right away.


P2RE ® Crowdfunding

The project is posted to the website, where accredited investors and financial professionals access the project details and make an investment.


Reporting

Tracking, legal, tax, and regulatory filing on your dashboard.
We're an open book. No secrets, surprises or hidden fees for anyone.


Repeat!

Our short term investments mean investors can turn money around into a new project and real estate operators can bring new projects to the platform.







