Patch of Land, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 2:44 AM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of Patch of Land, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Patch of Land, Inc. is a peer-to-real-estate lending marketplace that matches accredited and institutional investors seeking high-yield, short-term, and asset-collateralized investments to borrowers seeking sources of funding for rehabbing properties across America. It serves accredited, institutional, and international investors. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Los Angeles, California.


1964 Westwood BoulevardSuite 350Los Angeles, CA 90025United StatesFounded in 2013



Phone: 888-959-1465

Fax: 310-776-6484

www.patchofland.com







Key Executives for Patch of Land, Inc.




