Patch of Land Launches Mid Term Product



May 24, 2016
The Executive Branch



    

 
Share this Article Facebook Twitter
Email LinkedIn Google+ 




Patch of Land's Mid Term Offering is an entirely new product offering to meet the demands and expectations of both our Real Estate Entrepreneurs and Investors alike.
As Real Estate Entrepreneurs, our Mid Term product offers 2 to 3 year terms, funding in as little as 7 days, and rates starting at 7%. As Investors, our Mid Term product provides more stabilized properties at attractive rates and returns of up to 9%, over longer periods.
Whether you're a Real Estate Entrepreneur or Investor on Patch of Land, the Mid Term Offering can help better suit your real estate investment needs. 
Click here to learn more about the Mid Term as a Real Estate Entrepreneur.
Click here to get all the facts about the Mid Term as an Investor.

 
